headline: TMA Systems Completes Workday Design Approved Integration
summary: TULSA, Okla., November 18, 2025--TMA Systems launches Workday-approved WebTMA integration, uniting finance and asset data for real-time insights and streamlined operations.

headline: Microsoft unveils tool to help companies control, track AI agents
summary: Microsoft has helped companies build AI agents that can do specific kinds of work. Now it has a way to spot and stop risky agents.
